&lt;li&gt;Develop secure and efficient REST APIs within Legion&#39;s API-driven ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure high-performance, reliable integrations using modern cloud platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with architects and engineers for design collaboration and code reviews.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve development practices and stay ahead of agile software engineering trends.&lt;/li&gt;
