&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PREFERRED QUALIFICATIONS AND ATTRIBUTES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with observability tools such as Datadog, CloudWatch, ELK stack, Prometheus, or similar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing AWS RDS and/or Aurora MySQL including slow query analysis, replication, and upgrade operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience implementing SLIs/SLOs and reliability best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working effectively with remote, distributed teams.&lt;/li&gt;
