&lt;li&gt;Maintain deep familiarity with each customer’s environment, priorities, and use cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Expertise &amp;amp; Consultation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
